    "\", p.6 3 Chen and Bellavitis [78] Compromised privacy \"Second, although transparency is a cornerstone of decentralized platforms and distributed trust, extreme transparency may jeopardize privacy.",
    "\", p.6 3 Chen and Bellavitis [78] User unfriendliness \"[…] many projects tend to focus on technical advancement rather than usefulness and user-friendliness.",
